Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:03.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:08.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,During the battle surrounding Nirvana \Nwith Oracion Seis, Erza fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:11.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then we lost Lyon...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:16.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to take back the \Nkidnapped Wendy, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:19.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Jellal here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:28.67,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's love and dreams and you it'll become magical.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:35.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's cast a smile spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:48.77,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of admired this powerful world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:53.19,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,chock-full of problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:59.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Frozen time has started to move again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:05.58,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,ever since I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:11.00,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were we born? Why do we live?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:16.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any complicated answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:22.78,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Laugh! Cry! Be honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:27.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Simple feelings are the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:35.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You can change those tears shed on sad nights into strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:42.53,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's cast a smile spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:04.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:47.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:02:59.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:04.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... Lyon-sama has...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:06.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that guy's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:07.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's search for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:09.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Lyon-sama have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is to blame?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:35.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you are here. Show yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:43.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from one of the \NTen Great Wizard Saints.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:02.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My magic softens the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:05.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And your magic hardens the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:06.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:12.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, which one is stronger, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:16.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, it is not the \Nsuperior magic that counts,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but the one with the stronger ideals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:23.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner, since time immemorial,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:25.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is the one with the money, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:45.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd this happen? Suddenly a map \Nto this place popped into my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:48.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, hurry and wake Wendy-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:49.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:53.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, save Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:07.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:15.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:19.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's been bitten by a poisonous snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:21.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save her! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:24.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:36.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We need Erza-san's strength \Nto fight Oracion Seis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:39.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, save Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:41.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:46.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Yes, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:49.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to be splayed \Nout like that? It's unbecoming...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:08.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Jellal would do such \Na horrible thing to Erza-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:15.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:32.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I can't hear this guy's thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:37.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could hear his thoughts, I \Nwouldn't have to follow him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a place like this in the Woodsea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:24.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be like Brain said? \NIs this where Nirvana...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:49.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally we've found it! Our future!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:57.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished. All the poison is \Ngone from Erza-san's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, high-five!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:15.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:30.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She might not wake up for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But she'll be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Her complexion is returning to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:38.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Sky Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:40.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:44.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please refrain from using \NWendy's Sky Magic any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:49.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, it uses up a \Nlot of Wendy's magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:53.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:57.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After Erza-san wakes up, it's \Ntime to launch a counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We'll K.O. those Oracion Seis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:05.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We ain't gonna let 'em have Nirvana!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:07.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:22.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A pillar of black light...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:00.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... Nirvana!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:19.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got it! We got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:23.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... It's ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:41.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Could that be Nirvana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:41.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:45.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There is no mistaking it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:49.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:53.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guild wizards will all be wiped out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:55.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...before midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:59.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, you head toward that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Nirvana?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:08.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was awakened by Oracion Seis first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That light...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:20.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal is there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:23.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:32.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:39.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I... It's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let them meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let Erza see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:54.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... will... crush him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What could that light be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:13.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. Something is flowing out \Nfrom that eerie "black tree."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like it's being sucked into that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:23.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Nirvana is at the \Nplace where that light is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:27.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, that means \Nsomeone already found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:31.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the alliance? Or Oracion Seis?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiki, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:37.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Hibiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:41.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magical power must be \Nblocking communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:44.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:47.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep searching for Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:50.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'll head toward that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:58.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... What in the world is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:07.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault was it that Lyon-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:14.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Lyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:17.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:24.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:26.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:30.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:33.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The main body has not yet started up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:36.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is only the seal being released.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:40.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this definitely \Nsmells like money to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:41.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:46.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no time to fight this guy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:51.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the mission is to \Nsuppress Oracion Seis...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:55.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight? Or stop Nirvana?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Money! Money!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:03.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we will become rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:20.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go after Natsu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:21.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say something about Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:26.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later! We \Nhave to go after Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:29.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:35.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't even thank Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:41.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza... Maybe she heard \Nthe name Jellal, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:42.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:45.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:55.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I healed Jellal, they found \NNirvana, and Erza-san and Natsu-san are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:04.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:11.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:19.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show you the power of \NRacer's personal guild, Harpyia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:21.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:24.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:31.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let him get near Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for shocking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:41.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But all I did was knock her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But why? And why are we running?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading after Natsu-kun and Erza-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:47.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head toward the light as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not buying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:53.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Wendy's a whiner, but that is \Nno reason to treat her so roughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:54.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:04.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:07.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know about the magic called "Nirvana."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:09.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:14.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't tell anyone its true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:18.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This magic is very dangerous when \Nyou know about it consciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:23.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Ichiya-san and \Neven Ren and Eve don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:26.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only I was told by the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an extremely fearsome magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:34.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It switches light for darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:36.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Nirvana...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:39.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Light and darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It switches them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:44.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the final stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:48.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When the seal is first released, \Nblack light rises up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:50.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:51.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First there's the black light...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:57.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The people in between the light and the \Ndarkness switch to the opposite element.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:03.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of light who feel \Npowerful negative emotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:08.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...fall into darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:13.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the reason you put Wendy to sleep was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:18.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault! It's because I healed Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:22.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling guilt is a negative emotion, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:26.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At that rate, Wendy-chan might \Nhave fallen into darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:29.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment. Then, what about anger?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:33.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:37.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:42.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that anger is for someone else's sake, I \Nwouldn't necessarily call it a negative emotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:46.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do? I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:52.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, when the \Nseal on Nirvana is lifted,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:55.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,those who are motivated by justice or evil
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:58.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,have their personality switched, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:02.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I kept silent about \Nthe type of magic it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:09.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When people become focused on \Nthe good and evil of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:11.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it gives rise to unimaginable \Nnegative emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:15.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"If it wasn't for him..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:18.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Whose fault is it that I suffer like this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:20.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why is it always me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:25.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those thoughts will all be judged by Nirvana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:27.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:46.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have attacked the enemy, Lyon-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:52.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His friends, Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:57.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Money! Money! Money! Money!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:03.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Money!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:06.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have no need for such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:07.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:14.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been all frantic about \Nmy long-lost brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:18.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought... If only I had \Nmoney, I could find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:19.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:23.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have realized, I took it too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:25.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:29.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I have decided to no longer fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:30.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:34.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fill the world with love! Yes, love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:37.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A word that just overflows \Nwith sweetness and compassion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:41.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there is love in this \Nworld, nothing is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:42.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:47.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us stop the violent \Nacts of my former allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:50.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall teach them the wonders of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:51.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:54.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:20:59.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,White Fury!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:15.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The hunt has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:18.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My magic won't hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:26.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.11,0:21:33.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:39.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So if Nirvana fully activates, \Nwe'll all become bad guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:45.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But in that case, wouldn't the people \Nfrom the Dark Guilds turn into good guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:53.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truly fearsome power of Nirvana \Nlies in the ability to control it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:59.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, if you used \NNirvana against a guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:03.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The allies could kill each \Nother without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.87,0:22:06.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They could go to war with \Nother guilds for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.21,0:22:08.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting things like that \Nwould be child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:09.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:12.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop it at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.30,0:22:19.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to wipe out \Nall the light guilds!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.63,0:23:58.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... I think you'd be red.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:00.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What're you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.13,0:24:02.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The color that fits your image!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:04.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You use flames, so you're red.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.33,0:24:07.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray uses ice, so I guess \Nthat makes him blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:10.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy... You're givin' away your own color?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.92,0:24:14.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right! W-What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:16.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Spirit vs. Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.50,0:24:19.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about I be \Nsomething cool like black?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:20.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Black is totally Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.37,0:24:23.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's definitely got the blackest \Npersonality in Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.88,0:24:26.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
